Hide
Screen Open 0,320,200,16,Lowres
Colour 0,$111
Colour 1,$F40
Colour 2,$FD0
Cls 0
Ink 1
Bar 0,0 To 23,23
Ink 2
Bar 6,6 To 17,17
Get Bob 1,0,0 To 24,24
Cls 0
X=40
Y=88
Do
   If Jright(1) Then Add X,3
   If Jleft(1) Then Add X,-3
   If Jup(1) Then Add Y,-3
   If Jdown(1) Then Add Y,3
   Bob 1,X,Y,1
   Wait Vbl
Loop
